snippet.title: Gua-Le-Ni: Official Trailer (2011 RELEASE)
snippet.description: http://www.gua-le-ni.com ~ Double Jungle's 'Gua-Le-Ni' (iPad, 2011) is the first commercially-released casual video game whose development and tuning were guided by the analysis of its players' psychophysiological responses.
